"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/748116","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-07-10","<p>RAF Henlow has been identified for disposal in accordance with the Department's standard procedures as mandated by the Treasury but has not yet been sold.</p><p>The future of the site is subject to on-going detailed assessment work.</p><p>The Department is aware of a proposal to develop the site as a science innovation and technology park, but no formal discussions on this topic have taken place or offers made.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-07-10T15:50:44.387Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/748116/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/748116/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/748116/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-04","RAF Henlow","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how much revenue his Department will receive from the sale of land at RAF Henlow for the construction of the proposed science, innovation and technology park at that site.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","2908"
